    whyItMatters: "The fontes moralitatis provide the definitive Catholic framework for moral evaluation, preventing both rigid legalism (ignoring intention and circumstances) and situational relativism (ignoring the object).",
    relatedTerms: ["intrinsic-evil", "double-effect", "veritatis-splendor", "conscience"]
